  <summary>&lt;p>Infinite customization for the KDE Plasma panels.&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>Presets&lt;/b>&lt;br />&lt;em> 30+ built-in presets&lt;br />&lt;/em> Create your own configuration presets&lt;br />&lt;em> Restore defaults&lt;br />&lt;/em> Preset auto-loading&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Floating panel&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Maximized window shown&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>Widget Background&lt;/b>&lt;br />&lt;em> Color modes&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Static&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Animated&lt;br />&lt;/em> -&amp;gt; Interval&lt;br />&lt;em> -&amp;gt; Fading&lt;br />&lt;/em> Colors&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Custom&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; System&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Custom list&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Random&lt;br />&lt;em> Contrast correction&lt;br />&lt;/em> Style&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Spacing&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Margin rules&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Border radius&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Outline&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Opacity&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Shadow&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Line mode&lt;br />&lt;/em> Image / Color gradient background&lt;br />&lt;em> Widget islands&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>Icons and text&lt;/b>&lt;br />&lt;/em> Color Modes&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Static&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Interval&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Follow widget background&lt;br />&lt;/em> Colors&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Custom&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; System&lt;br />&lt;em> &amp;bull; Custom list&lt;br />&lt;/em> &amp;bull; Random&lt;br />&lt;em> Contrast correction&lt;br />&lt;/em> Opacity&lt;br />&lt;em> Blacklisted widgets color&lt;br />&lt;/em> Force icon color to on specific plasmoids that use Kirigami.Icon&lt;br />&lt;em> Recolor applications tray icon&lt;br />&lt;/em> Replace system tray icons&lt;br />&lt;em> Icons/text shadow&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>Panel background&lt;/b>&lt;br />&lt;/em> Opacity&lt;br />&lt;em> Color&lt;br />&lt;/em> Border radius&lt;br />&lt;em> Outline&lt;br />&lt;/em> Constant floating panel side padding&lt;br />&lt;em> Shadow&lt;br />&lt;/em> Transparent panel&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>Other&lt;/b>&lt;br />* Widget Blacklist&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>Support the development ❤️&lt;/b>&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;/p>&lt;ul>&lt;li> GitHub Sponsors &lt;a href="https://github.com/sponsors/luisbocanegra">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://github.com/sponsors/luisbocanegra">https://github.com/sponsors/luisbocanegra&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;/li>&lt;li> Ko-fi &lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/luisbocanegra">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/luisbocanegra">https://ko-fi.com/luisbocanegra&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;/li>&lt;li> Buy Me A Coffee &lt;a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/luisbocanegra">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/luisbocanegra">https://www.buymeacoffee.com/luisbocanegra&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;/li>&lt;li> PayPal &lt;a href="https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=Y5TMH3Z4YZRDA">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=Y5TMH3Z4YZRDA">https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=Y5TMH3Z4YZRDA&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;/li>&lt;li> Liberapay &lt;a href="https://liberapay.com/luisbocanegra/">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://liberapay.com/luisbocanegra/">https://liberapay.com/luisbocanegra/&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;/li>&lt;/ul></summary>
