  <summary>&lt;p>Plasmoid for monitoring CPU, memory, network traffic, GPUs and disks IO.&lt;br />&lt;br />Looking for plasma 5 ?  Please see &lt;a href="https://www.pling.com/p/1527636/">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.pling.com/p/1527636/">https://www.pling.com/p/1527636/&lt;/a>.&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>&lt;u>REQUIRED DEPENDENCIES&lt;/u>&lt;/b> :&lt;br />- &lt;b>libksysguard&lt;/b> (normally include by default) : This is for retrieving  most of metrics.&lt;br />&lt;b>Opional dependencies&lt;/b> :&lt;br />- &lt;b>plasma-addons&lt;/b> (or similar name) : This is only required if you want select an application to run.&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>&lt;u>LOVE THIS PROJECT ?&lt;/u>&lt;/b>&lt;br />Think to &lt;a href="https://www.paypal.me/orblazer">sponsor me on PayPal&lt;/a> for help me to maintain that project !&lt;/p></summary>
